    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275676</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオス、言ったよな、
インネンがなんとかって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos said it was our fate...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275748</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>因縁を追え、だよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So we should chase after our fate.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275904</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスと
あの仮面のヤツって
関係あんのかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I feel Dhaos and the masked
two are related, somehow...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275904</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;は、
なんか心当たりないのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you know of anything about this, &lt;Rody&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276148</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あんな仮面してたら
あいつらが誰かわかんないし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I really have no idea who those masked guys are.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276148</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それに……あいつ、
肝心なこと、あんま
話さなかったしな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Plus, it's not like that guy...really talked
much about important things.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276320</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それどころか、私が
ほとんど一方的に
話してた気がする</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I seriously had to squeeze the information
outta the guy. As I said, we had one-sided
conversations.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>夢中になっていろいろ
話した覚えはあるんだけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I remember our many converstations,
but they're hazy like a dream.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276640</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あはは、肝心の話の中身が
全然思い出せないや</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I remember we talked about a lot of stuff.
Though...ahaha, I can't really remember
any of the important parts.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276704</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ、それ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wow, that sucks.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、空の星には
たくさんの種類があって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh...he said in the sky there
are many other worlds...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ってこれ、
ダオスがしてた話だし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Or so he said.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>276916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんか、あいつのしてた話は
よく覚えてんだよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>For some reason, I remember our
small talk more than anything.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277028</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>太陽の周りを回るアセリアは遊星、
その周りを回るのが衛星だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aselia orbits around our great sun, in
turn, a wandering planet orbits around
Aselia. This is called a satellite.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277108</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>デリス・カーラーンは衛星？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Derris Kharlan is a satellite planet?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277188</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>デリス・カーラーンは彗星だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Derris Kharlan is a comet.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277248</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>彗星？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A comet?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277420</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>純然たるマナの塊星（かたまりぼし）</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It is a celestial body almost entirely
composed of pure Mana.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277420</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ガス化したマナは
太陽から吹く風を受けて
尾を引き、彗星になる……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mana that becomes gas leaves a trail
when it contacts solar wind. Therefore,
it is considered a comet...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277496</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>へぇ……綺麗なんだろうね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wow! That sounds so pretty!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>１００年に１度、我が母星は
このアセリアに近づく</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Every 100 years, my home world
approaches Aselia's orbit.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この星から見えるのは
５０年以上も先のことだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You'll be able to see it from this
planet in about 50 years.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277748</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その頃、私、
もうおばあちゃんだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aw, but by that time I'll
be a wrinkly old woman!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278028</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスは初め全然、
話してくれなくて、
ずっと私だけが喋ってたけど</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>At first Dhaos didn't talk at all and
I had to do all the talking, but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278028</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>少しずつ、本当に少しずつ
自分のことを話すようになった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>One step at a time...He gradually
started opening up to me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278028</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>デリス・カーラーンとか、
『大いなる実り』とか、
旅の苦難とかのことを……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He talked about Derris Kharlan... His
voyage to this planet, his suffering
and how he needed the Mana Seed...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その話を聞いて、
私はダオスのために何か
してあげたいって思った</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I was always so anxious for our next
conversation. I'd have given anything
to talk to him back then.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『大いなる実り』を、
なんとかしてあげたかったんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'd have done anything to give him a Mana Seed...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278680</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスと仮面の連中の話だったのに、
つまんない話になっちゃったね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Woops, there I go ranting. In short,
I don't know how the masked guys
and Dhaos are related.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278796</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いえ……いつかちゃんと
ダオスに会って話が聞ければ
……いいですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, please...hearing about your
talks with Dhaos has been nice.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>次、会って何も言わねーで
逃げやがったら、オレらで
とっ捕まえてやるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's catch him next time so
we can get the full picture!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279004</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ありがと、
双子ちゃんはいい子だね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You two really are a fair pair of twins!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>32</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279064</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Hehe~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>33</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279136</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_280_015_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さっ、先に進もうぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All right, time to cut the
chit chat and get going!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>34</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
